name: 2023 In Review - An Aviation Short Film
description:
Hi everyone! As some of you might remember, I try to end each year with a special video of sorts, looking back at some of the best moments.

In 2023's case, there were quite a lot, and it is genuinely because of you watching, and especially my channel members, that I'm able to make these videos at all.

I'm very grateful for your continued support, it really doesn't go unnoticed and I have a ton of projects coming up that I think you'll like.

This next year should be an interesting one, so as always, thank you so much for watching, and I'll see you in 2024!

Music is "Rise" by Martynas Lau (Whitesand): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6gkx6sUZ2hc
